text: A dinamuna nivu visvasulaina purusulanu mariyu visvasulaina strilanu custe, vari velugu, vari mundu nundi mariyu vari kudi vaipu nundi parigettutu untundi. (Varito ila anabadutundi): "I roju miku krinda selayerlu pravahince svargavanala subhavarta ivvabadutondi, mirandulo sasvatanga untaru! Ide a goppa vijayam
